main event: An unidentified flying object, described as a slightly elliptical metallic echo, was observed moving rapidly at Tyndall AFB, Florida on May 9, 1961.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 50-60 seconds., The object appeared to undergo rapid acceleration and extensive maneuvering., Witnesses initially thought it was the satellite Echo., The angular velocity of the object was reported as rapid., It disappeared on a southwest heading at a 45-degree angle.
witness description: A civilian and two military personnel observed the UFO.
